import React from "react"; const Weather = (props) => (
{ props.city &&

City: {props.city}, {props.country}

T: {props.temp_max} °С

T: {props.temp_min} °С

Sunrise: {props.sunrise}

Sunset: {props.sunset}

Cloudiness: {props.weather_description}

Wind: {props.wind} m/s

Humidity: {props.clouds} %

Pressure: {props.pressure} hpa

}

{ props.error }

) export default Weather;
